{"page_id":"512","title":"Multiplex Assay Services | Interactive Panel Selector","identifier":"services/multiplex-assay-services","content_heading":"","update_time":"2026-04-11 12:55:45","content":"            <section class=\"mb-6 text-center hero-section\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/media/images/design-guide/hero-people-team2.jpg&quot;);\">\n            <div class=\"dark-overlap\">\n              <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-lg-8 text-left\">\n                  <p class=\"font-large mb-4 font-weight-bold\">EXPERT BIOMARKER ANALYSIS</p>\n                  <h1 class=\"mb-2\">Multiplex Assay Service</h1>\n                  <p class=\"font-large mb-4\">Maximize productivity with expert scientists delivering fast, reliable multiplex cytokine assay results. Our comprehensive Luminex multiplex cytokine assay service offers customizable panels, low-volume requirements, and validated platforms for superior biomarker detection.</p><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/services/multiplex-assay-services/panel-details\" class=\"btn-orange\">Browse Available Panels</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-lg-4 text-left\">\n                  <p class=\"font-large mb-4 font-weight-bold\">Begin Inquiry</p>\n                  <form id=\"boster-form\" action=\"https://bioinvsync.com/zohobooksAPI/api.php\" method=\"post\" redirecturl=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER\">\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" name=\"action\" value=\"createOpportunity\" hidden=\"true\" required=\"\">\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" name=\"opportunity_name\" value=\"Multiplex Assay Service Inquiry\" hidden=\"true\" required=\"\">\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" name=\"description\" value=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/services/multiplex-assay-services\" hidden=\"true\" required=\"\">\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" name=\"opportunity_type\" value=\"Multiplex Assay Service\" hidden=\"true\" required=\"\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                      <div class=\"form-group col-md-6\"><label for=\"input-6\">First Name*</label>\n                        <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" name=\"firstname\" id=\"input-6\" placeholder=\"e.g. Diana\" required=\"\">\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"form-group col-md-6\"><label for=\"input-6\">Last Name*</label>\n                        <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" name=\"lastname\" id=\"input-6\" placeholder=\"e.g. Prince\" required=\"\">\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"form-group\"><label for=\"input-8\">Phone*</label>\n                      <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"tel\" name=\"phone\" id=\"input-8\" placeholder=\"1(510)511-9222\" required=\"\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"form-group\"><label for=\"input-9\">Email*</label>\n                      <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"email\" name=\"email\" id=\"input-9\" placeholder=\"example@test.com\" required=\"\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"form-group\"><label for=\"input-10\">Inquiry details*</label>\n                      <textarea class=\"form-control\" type=\"textarea\" name=\"original_inquiry\" id=\"input-10\" placeholder=\"tell us about your needs and requirements.\" required=\"\"></textarea>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"btn-orange\" onclick=\"submitInquiryForm(this)\">Get a Quote</p>\n                  </form>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n                \n            </div>\n          </section>\n    <!-- Credibility Banner -->\n    <section class=\"mt-6 topic-heading-section full-width-section\" id=\"service-overview\">\n            <div class=\"text-center p-3\" style=\"\">\n              <div class=\"dark-overlap px-5 py-6 \" style=\"background-image: url(https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/media/images/design-guide/black-background.jpg);\">\n                <div class=\"container\">\n                  <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12\">\n                      <div class=\"d-flex justify-content-lg-between justify-content-center flex-column flex-lg-row\">\n                        <div class=\"p-3 border-rounded single-item flex-1 mb-3 mb-lg-0\">\n                          <div class=\"single-credibility-item-icon border-circled m-auto\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-th font-largest\"></i>\n                          </div>\n                          <p class=\"mt-3\"><b>PhD-level scientists</b><br>Expert consultation &amp; support<br></p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"p-3 border-rounded single-item flex-1 mb-3 mb-lg-0\">\n                          <div class=\"single-credibility-item-icon border-circled m-auto\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-calendar font-largest\"></i>\n                          </div>\n                          <p class=\"mt-3\"><b>Fast turnaround</b><br>Quick decision-making</p></div>\n                        <div class=\"p-3 border-rounded single-item flex-1 mb-3 mb-lg-0\">\n                          <div class=\"single-credibility-item-icon border-circled m-auto\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-star font-largest\"></i>\n                          </div>\n                          <p class=\"mt-3\"><b>Competitive pricing</b><br>Excellent value</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"p-3 border-rounded single-item flex-1 mb-3 mb-lg-0\">\n                          <div class=\"single-credibility-item-icon border-circled m-auto\">\n                            <i class=\"boster-icon icon-antibodies font-largest\"></i>\n                          </div>\n                          <p class=\"mt-3\"><b>Comprehensive data</b><br>Actionable insights</p>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"#inquiry\" class=\"btn-orange mt-4 mr-4\">Request a Quote</a>\n              <p class=\"text-grey text-center mx-auto mb-5 font-medium\" style=\"max-width: 700px;\"><br></p>\n            </div>\n          </section>\n    <!-- Section Header -->\n    <section class=\"default-template mb-5\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-orange text-center font-larger text-uppercase font-weight-bold mb-3\">Why Choose Our Multiplex Assay Service?</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-grey text-center w-75 mx-auto mb-5 font-medium\">Our multiplex cytokine assay service combines advanced Luminex technology with expert scientific support to deliver comprehensive biomarker analysis with minimal sample requirements.</p>\n    </section>\n    <!-- Three Column Cards with Icons -->\n    <section class=\"default-template mb-6\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3); border-radius: 4px;\">\n        <div class=\"container p-3\" style=\"\n    display: table;\n\">\n            <div class=\"multicolumns\">\n                <div class=\"table-cell col-md-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-4 border-rounded border text-center\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-orange font-large\">Expert Scientists</h3>\n                        <div class=\"medium-icon-container bg-orange\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-user-tie\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <p>Maximize productivity by working with our team of PhD-level scientists who provide expert consultation throughout your project. Our experienced staff ensures accurate assay selection, optimal sample preparation, and reliable data interpretation for your multiplex cytokine assays.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"table-cell col-md-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-4 border-rounded border text-center\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-orange font-large\">Customizable Options</h3>\n                        <div class=\"medium-icon-container bg-orange\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-cogs\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <p>Our multiplex assay service offers flexible panel design to match your specific research needs. Choose from pre-configured cytokine multiplex assay luminex panels or create custom combinations from our extensive biomarker library including cytokines, chemokines, growth factors, and more.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"table-cell col-md-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-4 border-rounded border text-center\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-orange font-large\">Advanced Technology</h3>\n                        <div class=\"medium-icon-container bg-orange\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-microscope\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <p>Leverage cutting-edge Luminex xMAP technology for superior results. Our validated luminex multiplex cytokine assay platforms deliver high sensitivity, broad dynamic range, and simultaneous detection of up to 100 analytes from a single sample.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <!-- Comprehensive Service Offerings -->\n    <section class=\"default-template mb-6 selected\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3); border-radius: 4px;\">\n        <div class=\"container p-3\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-orange text-center font-larger text-uppercase font-weight-bold mb-3\">Comprehensive Service Offerings</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-grey text-center w-75 mx-auto mb-5 font-medium\">From sample processing to data analysis, we provide end-to-end multiplex cytokine assay services tailored to your research goals.</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"multicolumns\">\n                <div class=\"table-cell col-md-3\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-4 border-rounded border text-center\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-orange font-large\">Luminex Cytokine Panel</h3>\n                        <p>Comprehensive cytokine profiling using validated luminex cytokine assay panels. Detect dozens of inflammatory markers, interleukins, and chemokines simultaneously with industry-leading sensitivity.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"table-cell col-md-3\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-4 border-rounded border text-center\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-orange font-large\">Custom Panels</h3>\n                        <p>Design your own multiplex cytokine assay panels from our extensive biomarker library. Mix and match targets relevant to your specific disease model or therapeutic area of interest.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"table-cell col-md-3\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-4 border-rounded border text-center\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-orange font-large\">Sample Testing</h3>\n                        <p>Professional sample testing service with minimal volume requirements. We accept serum, plasma, cell culture supernatants, and tissue lysates with protocols optimized for each matrix.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"table-cell col-md-3\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-4 border-rounded border text-center\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-orange font-large\">Data Analysis</h3>\n                        <p>Comprehensive data analysis and interpretation included with every project. Receive detailed reports with statistical analysis, quality control metrics, and publication-ready figures.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <!-- Key Advantages Section -->\n    <section class=\"default-template mb-6\" style=\"\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-lg-6 mb-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-lightgrey p-4 border-rounded\" style=\"height: 100%;\">\n                        <h3 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-3\">Sample Efficiency &amp; Low-Volume Requirements</h3>\n                        <p class=\"mb-3\">Our multiplex cytokine assay service requires minimal sample volume while delivering maximum data output. Analyze up to 100 biomarkers from as little as 25-50 µL of sample, making it ideal for precious specimens or studies with limited material availability.</p>\n                        <p class=\"mb-3\"><strong>Key Benefits:</strong></p>\n                        <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                            <li>✓ Minimal sample consumption (25-50 µL per test)</li>\n                            <li>✓ Simultaneous multi-analyte detection</li>\n                            <li>✓ Preserve valuable samples for additional studies</li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-lg-6 mb-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-lightgrey p-4 border-rounded\" style=\"height: 100%;\">\n                        <h3 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-3\">Validated Platforms</h3>\n                        <p class=\"mb-3\">All our luminex multiplex cytokine assay platforms undergo rigorous validation to ensure compliance with regulatory standards. Our quality management system guarantees reproducible, reliable results you can trust for publication and regulatory submissions.</p>\n                        <p class=\"mb-3\"><strong>Quality Assurance:</strong></p>\n                        <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                            <li>✓ Comprehensive validation documentation</li>\n                            <li>✓ Inter- and intra-assay CV &lt; 15%</li>\n                            <li>✓ Extensive QC at every step</li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <!-- Two Column Content with Card -->\n    <section class=\"default-template mb-6 bg-lightgrey p-5\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-lg-8 p-3\">\n                    <h3 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-2\">Diverse Biomarker Capabilities</h3>\n                    <h4 class=\"font-medium text-grey mb-4\">Comprehensive multiplex cytokine assay panels covering all major biological pathways</h4>\n                    <p class=\"mb-4\">Our multiplex assay service provides access to an extensive library of validated biomarkers. Whether you're studying inflammation, immunity, metabolism, or cancer biology, we offer the right luminex cytokine panel for your research.</p>\n                    \n                    <h4 class=\"font-medium\">Available Biomarker Categories:</h4>\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                            <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                                <li>• Cytokines &amp; Interleukins</li>\n                                <li>• Chemokines</li>\n                                <li>• Growth Factors</li>\n                            </ul>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                            <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                                <li>• Adipokines</li>\n                                <li>• Angiogenesis Markers</li>\n                                <li>• Metabolic Markers</li>\n                            </ul>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                            <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                                <li>• Cancer Biomarkers</li>\n                                <li>• Cardiovascular Markers</li>\n                                <li>• Soluble Receptors</li>\n                            </ul>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <a href=\"#inquiry\" class=\"btn-orange mr-4 mt-3\">Explore Biomarkers</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-lg-4 p-3\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-orange p-4 border-rounded text-white\">\n                        <h3 class=\"font-large mb-3\">Fast Turnaround Time</h3>\n                        <p style=\"font-size: 9rem; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;\">⚡</p>\n                        <p class=\"mb-3\">Speed matters in research. Our streamlined multiplex cytokine assay service delivers results in as little as 1-2 weeks from sample receipt, enabling quick decision-making for your project timeline.</p>\n                        <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Standard turnaround: 10-14 business days</strong></p>\n                        <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Rush service available upon request</strong></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <!-- Service Process Steps -->\n    <section class=\"default-template mb-6\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-orange text-center font-larger text-uppercase font-weight-bold mb-3 mt-6\">Our Straightforward Service Process</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-grey text-center w-75 mx-auto mb-5 font-medium\">From consultation to data delivery, we've streamlined every step to make your multiplex assay service experience seamless and efficient.</p>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-lg-2 col-md-12\"></div>\n                <div class=\"col-lg-8 col-md-12\">\n                    <div class=\"timeline-bubbles\">\n                        <ul>\n                            <li>\n                                <h3 class=\"font-large\">Step 1: Consultation &amp; Design</h3>\n                                <p class=\"font-medium\">Connect with our PhD-level scientists to discuss your research objectives. We'll help you select the optimal luminex cytokine panel or design a custom multiplex cytokine assay tailored to your specific biomarkers of interest.</p>\n                            </li>\n                            <li>\n                                <h3 class=\"font-large\">Step 2: Sample Submission</h3>\n                                <p class=\"font-medium\">Ship your samples using our convenient sample submission kit. We accept various sample types including serum, plasma, cell culture supernatants, and tissue lysates. Our team provides detailed sample preparation guidelines to ensure optimal results.</p>\n                            </li>\n                            <li>\n                                <h3 class=\"font-large\">Step 3: Assay Execution</h3>\n                                <p class=\"font-medium\">Your samples are processed using validated luminex multiplex cytokine assay protocols on state-of-the-art instrumentation. Every run includes appropriate controls and standards to ensure data quality and reproducibility.</p>\n                            </li>\n                            <li>\n                                <h3 class=\"font-large\">Step 4: Quality Control</h3>\n                                <p class=\"font-medium\">Comprehensive QC analysis is performed on all data. We evaluate standard curves, blank values, spike recoveries, and replicate precision to ensure your results meet the highest quality standards.</p>\n                            </li>\n                            <li>\n                                <h3 class=\"font-large\">Step 5: Data Delivery &amp; Analysis</h3>\n                                <p class=\"font-medium\">Receive your comprehensive report including raw data, analyzed results, statistical analysis, and quality control metrics. Our easy-to-use data format facilitates quick decision-making and integrates seamlessly with your workflow.</p>\n                            </li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <!-- Competitive Pricing CTA -->\n    <section class=\"default-template mb-6 p-3 bg-orange\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-lg-8 col-12\">\n                    <h3 class=\"font-large text-white\">Competitive Pricing for Multiplex Assay Service</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-white\">Get excellent value without compromising quality. Our transparent pricing structure includes all aspects of the multiplex cytokine assay service from sample processing to comprehensive data analysis. Volume discounts available for large projects.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-lg-4 col-12 vertical-center\">\n                    <a href=\"#inquiry\" class=\"btn-outline-white\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 300px;\">Request Pricing Quote</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <!-- Technology & Systems -->\n    <section class=\"default-template mb-6\" style=\"\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-orange text-center font-larger text-uppercase font-weight-bold mb-3\">Easy-to-Use Systems &amp; Software</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-grey text-center w-75 mx-auto mb-5 font-medium\">Our multiplex assay service leverages intuitive software platforms that deliver publication-ready data in user-friendly formats.</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-md-6 p-3\">\n                    <h3 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-2\">Advanced Luminex Platform</h3>\n                    <p class=\"mb-4\">We utilize the latest Luminex xMAP technology for our cytokine multiplex assay luminex services. This industry-leading platform provides unmatched sensitivity, reproducibility, and multiplexing capability for comprehensive biomarker analysis.</p>\n                    <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                        <li>✓ Up to 100-plex detection capability</li>\n                        <li>✓ Wide dynamic range (3-5 logs)</li>\n                        <li>✓ High sensitivity (sub-pg/mL detection)</li>\n                        <li>✓ Minimal cross-reactivity</li>\n                        <li>✓ Excellent reproducibility (CV &lt; 15%)</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-md-6 p-3\">\n                    <h3 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-2\">Comprehensive Data Package</h3>\n                    <p class=\"mb-4\">Every multiplex cytokine assay project includes a detailed data package designed for easy interpretation and analysis. Our reports facilitate quick decision-making with clearly presented results and quality metrics.</p>\n                    <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                        <li>✓ Raw and normalized data files</li>\n                        <li>✓ Standard curve analysis</li>\n                        <li>✓ Statistical analysis &amp; visualization</li>\n                        <li>✓ Quality control summary</li>\n                        <li>✓ Publication-ready figures</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <!-- Sample Types & Applications -->\n    <section class=\"default-template mb-6 bg-lightgrey p-5\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3); border-radius: 4px;\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-orange text-center font-larger text-uppercase font-weight-bold mb-3\">Versatile Sample Compatibility</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-grey text-center w-75 mx-auto mb-5 font-medium\">Our multiplex assay service accommodates diverse sample types across multiple research applications.</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 mb-4\">\n                    <h3 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-3\">Accepted Sample Types</h3>\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-4 border-rounded\">\n                        <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Human &amp; Animal Serum/Plasma</strong> - Most common sample type for luminex cytokine assay analysis</li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Cell Culture Supernatants</strong> - Ideal for in vitro cytokine production studies</li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Tissue Lysates</strong> - Analyze tissue-specific biomarker expression</li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Cerebrospinal Fluid (CSF)</strong> - Neuroinflammation and CNS studies</li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Saliva &amp; Urine</strong> - Non-invasive biomarker monitoring</li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 mb-4\">\n                    <h3 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-3\">Research Applications</h3>\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-4 border-rounded\">\n                        <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\">• Immunology &amp; Inflammation Studies</li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\">• Cancer &amp; Oncology Research</li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\">• Drug Discovery &amp; Development</li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\">• Biomarker Validation Studies</li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\">• Autoimmune Disease Research</li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\">• Cardiovascular Disease Studies</li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\">• Metabolic &amp; Endocrine Research</li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <!-- Providers/Recommendations Section -->\n    <section class=\"default-template mb-6\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3); border-radius: 4px;\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-orange text-center font-larger text-uppercase font-weight-bold mb-3\">Why Researchers Choose Our Multiplex Assay Service</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-grey text-center w-75 mx-auto mb-5 font-medium\">When you search for \"providers of multiplex assay service,\" you'll find many options. Here's what sets us apart as the preferred choice for cytokine multiplex assay luminex testing.</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-lg-4 mb-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-4 border-rounded border\" style=\"height: 100%;\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-orange font-large mb-3\"><i class=\"fas fa-trophy\"></i> Industry-Leading Expertise</h3>\n                        <p>Over 20 years of experience in multiplex cytokine assay services. Our team has supported thousands of successful research projects across academic, pharmaceutical, and biotech sectors worldwide.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-lg-4 mb-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-white p-4 border-rounded border selected\" style=\"height: 100%;\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-orange font-large mb-3\"><i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i> Superior Data Quality</h3>\n                        <p>Validated luminex multiplex cytokine assay protocols ensure reproducible, publication-grade results. Our stringent QC processes and expert data review guarantee the highest quality outpu